    {
      "node_id": "D009",
      "scene_id": "SC101",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "证据确凿，逮捕他！",
        "en": "The evidence is clear. Arrest him!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_decisive",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_005",
      "front_node": ["D006", "D007", "D008"],
      "next_node": "D010",
      "is_end": false,
      "narrative_function": "第一段对话高潮，Zack即将被捕"
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D010",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "慢着！这个人不是凶手！",
        "en": "Wait! This man is not the killer!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_determined",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_001",
      "front_node": "D009",
      "next_node": "D011",
      "is_end": false,
      "narrative_function": "Emma登场，转折点",
      "camera_effect": "scene_transition",
      "scene_change": {
        "from": "SC101",
        "to": "SC119"
      }
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D011",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "你是谁？",
        "en": "Who are you?"
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_surprised",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_006",
      "front_node": "D010",
      "next_node": "D012",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D012",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "《芝加哥先驱报》记者Emma O'Malley。我看到真凶从逃跑了！12点30分，一个黑衣男子离开现场！",
        "en": "Emma O'Malley, Chicago Herald reporter. I saw the real killer escape! At 12:30, a man in black left the scene!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_confident",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_002",
      "front_node": "D011",
      "next_node": "D013",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D013",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "你有什么证据？",
        "en": "What proof do you have?"
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_skeptical",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_007",
      "front_node": "D012",
      "next_node": "D014",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D014",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "我拍到了黑衣人的背影！",
        "en": "I photographed the man in black from behind!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_triumphant",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_003",
      "front_node": "D013",
      "next_node": "D015",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D015",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "Morrison警探，您来得太及时了。从案发到现场不到10分钟，除非您早知道会发生什么？",
        "en": "Detective Morrison, you arrived very promptly. Less than 10 minutes from the incident to your arrival. Unless you knew what would happen?"
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_questioning",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_004",
      "front_node": "D014",
      "next_node": "D016",
      "is_end": false,
      "narrative_function": "Emma质疑Morrison，暗示其可疑"
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D016",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "我接到匿名电话...",
        "en": "I received an anonymous call..."
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_defensive",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_008",
      "front_node": "D015",
      "next_node": "D017",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D017",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "那为什么不先调查现场，而是直接认定Brennan是凶手？",
        "en": "Then why didn't you investigate the scene first instead of immediately identifying Brennan as the killer?"
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_pressing",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_005",
      "front_node": "D016",
      "next_node": "D018",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D018",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "好吧...事情比我想象的复杂。但Brennan，别以为这样就能洗清嫌疑。",
        "en": "Alright... This is more complicated than I thought. But Brennan, don't think this clears your suspicion."
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_reluctant",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_009",
      "front_node": "D017",
      "next_node": "D019",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D019",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "我给你们三天时间。找不到真凶，我就逮捕你，Brennan。O'Malley，妨碍司法的罪名够你受的。",
        "en": "I'll give you three days. If you don't find the real killer, I'll arrest you, Brennan. O'Malley, obstruction of justice is a serious charge."
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_threatening",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_010",
      "front_node": "D018",
      "next_node": "D020",
      "is_end": false,
      "narrative_function": "设立72小时调查期限"
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D020",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "三天，72小时。时间一到，我亲自给你戴手铐！",
        "en": "Three days, 72 hours. When time's up, I'll put the handcuffs on you myself!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_menacing",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_011",
      "front_node": "D019",
      "next_node": "D021",
      "is_end": false
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D021",
      "scene_id": "SC119",
      "npc_id": "NPC004",
      "npc_name": "Morrison",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Morrison",
      "content": {
        "zh": "祈祷你们能找到那个黑衣人吧，否则Webb的死就算在你头上！",
        "en": "Pray you find that man in black, otherwise Webb's death will be on you!"
      },
      "character_portrait": "morrison_final_warning",
      "voice_file": "VO_Morrison_012",
      "front_node": "D020",
      "next_node": "D022",
      "is_end": true,
      "narrative_function": "Morrison离场，第二段对话结束"
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D022",
      "scene_id": "SC102",
      "npc_id": "NPC009",
      "npc_name": "Zack",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Zack",
      "content": {
        "zh": "谢谢你救了我。但我需要知道，你真的拍到了那个黑衣人吗？",
        "en": "Thank you for saving me. But I need to know, did you really photograph that man in black?"
      },
      "character_portrait": "zack_grateful_suspicious",
      "voice_file": "VO_Zack_001",
      "front_node": "D021",
      "next_node": "D023",
      "is_end": false,
      "narrative_function": "转场到街道，开始Emma与Zack的对话",
      "scene_change": {
        "from": "SC119",
        "to": "SC102"
      }
    },

    {
      "node_id": "D023",
      "scene_id": "SC102",
      "npc_id": "NPC010",
      "npc_name": "Emma",
      "dialog_type": "AVG",
      "speaker": "Emma",
      "content": {
        "zh": "我确实看到有人离开，也拍了照片。但说实话，照片很模糊，可能不足以在法庭上作为证据。不过足以让Morrison产生怀疑了。",
        "en": "I did see someone leave and took photos. But honestly, the photos are blurry and might not be sufficient as court evidence. But enough to make Morrison doubt."
      },
      "character_portrait": "emma_honest",
      "voice_file": "VO_Emma_006",
      "front_node": "D022",
      "next_node": "D024",
      "is_end": false
    }
